## Contribución

1. Crear feature branch: `git checkout -b feature/nueva-feature`
2. Hacer cambios y commit: `git commit -m 'Añade nueva feature'`
3. Push a la rama: `git push origin feature/nueva-feature`
4. Abrir Pull Request

